import { Grid, Card, Typography, CardContent, TextField} from "@mui/material";
export default function NewProduct() {
    return (
        <Grid container
            direction="column"
            alignItems="center"
            justifyContent="center"

        >
            <Grid item xs={3}>
                <Card
                    sx={{ mt: 5 }}
                >
                    <Typography>
                        New Product
                    </Typography>
                    <CardContent>
                        <form>
                            <TextField
                                variant="filled"
                                label="Product Name">

                            </TextField>
                            <TextField
                                variant="filled"
                                label="">

                            </TextField>
                        </form>
                    </CardContent>
                </Card>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    )
}
